org.pathvisio.core.model

Class PathwayEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pathvisio.core.model.PathwayEvent

  • public class PathwayEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to notify listeners of changes to the model, i.e a Pathway or PathwayElement. This can mean the addition or removal of whole elements, or just a modification to one of the properties of an existing element. This event is currently used both by PathwayListener's and PathwayElementListener's. That may change in the future.
